properties.pdsode:Footprint_souce: PDS Label Map Projection Bounding Box
properties.pdsode:Description: The first and second (X and Y) axes are projected distances corresponding to LINE and SAMPLE pixel directions. The third axis, DELAY_TIME, is referenced to a radius of 3392.2645 km. A FRAME consists of all values along the third axis for a given X and Y location. BACKSCATTER STRENGTH is the square root of backscatter power.
